, spermathecae, ventral view. 16. 
<taxonomicName class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Ami" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="2" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bladesi">
